#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"We are especially proud to present you Tails 5.0, the first version of Tails "
"based on Debian 11 (Bullseye). It brings new versions of a lot of the "
"software included in Tails and new OpenPGP tools."
msgstr ""
"Estem especialment orgullosos de presentar-vos Tails 5.0, la primera versió "
"de Tails basada en Debian 11 (Bullseye). Aporta noves versions de gran part "
"del programari inclòs a Tails i noves eines OpenPGP."

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "<h1 id=\"features\">New features</h1>\n"
msgstr "<h1 id=\"features\">Noves funcionalitats</h1>\n"

#. type: Title ##
#, no-wrap
msgid "Kleopatra"
msgstr "Kleopatra"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"We added [[*Kleopatra*|doc/encryption_and_privacy/kleopatra]] to replace the "
"*OpenPGP Applet* and the *Password and Keys* utility, also known as "
"*Seahorse*."
msgstr ""
"Hem afegit [[*Kleopatra*|doc/encryption_and_privacy/kleopatra]] per "
"substituir l'*Applet OpenPGP* i la utilitat *Contrasenya i claus*, també "
"coneguda com a *Seahorse*."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"The *OpenPGP Applet* was not actively developped anymore and was complicated "
"for us to keep in Tails. The *Password and Keys* utility was also poorly "
"maintained and Tails users suffered from too many of its issues until now, "
"like [[!tails_ticket 17183]]."
msgstr ""
"L'*Applet OpenPGP* ja no es desenvolupa activament i és complicat mantenir-"
"lo a Tails. La utilitat *Contrasenya i claus* tampoc s'està mantenint i els "
"usuaris de Tails patien massa problemes fins ara, com ara [[!tails_ticket "
"17183]]."

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"*Kleopatra* provides equivalent features in a single tool and is more\n"
"actively developed.\n"
msgstr ""
"*Kleopatra* ofereix funcions equivalents en una única eina i es\n"
"desenvolupa de manera més activa.\n"

